323
00:21:20,409 --> 00:21:22,368
Nice to meet you.

324
00:21:24,457 --> 00:21:26,763
Were you special forces?

325
00:21:26,807 --> 00:21:27,721
No.

326
00:21:27,764 --> 00:21:30,114
There's a junior
RotC group here

327
00:21:30,158 --> 00:21:31,551
