328
00:21:31,594 --> 00:21:33,335
Interested...

329
00:21:33,379 --> 00:21:34,728
Or not,

330
00:21:34,771 --> 00:21:37,034
if that's the case.

331
00:22:01,798 --> 00:22:04,061
O.k. If I join you?

332
00:22:11,025 --> 00:22:14,855
If I ate like that,
I'd be...

333
