about this trial by now.

338
00:22:35,876 --> 00:22:41,185
Maybe everybody's right
about me not testifying.

339
00:22:42,143 --> 00:22:43,449
No, they're not.

340
00:22:43,492 --> 00:22:44,885
If you
allow a student

341
