testify is wrong.

344
00:22:51,544 --> 00:22:53,894
Just like that?

345
00:22:53,937 --> 00:22:55,635
Just like that.

346
00:22:55,678 --> 00:22:56,897
You're in charge
of chaperons

347
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:59,900
