380
00:24:38,128 --> 00:24:38,999
You said...

381
00:24:39,042 --> 00:24:40,391
But you're not
acting like it.

382
00:24:40,435 --> 00:24:43,699
It's hard enough
without having to
fight you, too.

383
00:24:43,743 --> 00:24:45,309
I know that!

384
00:24:45,353 --> 00:24:49,313
Someone just
reminded me that this
is the right thing to do,

385
00:24:49,357 --> 00:24:52,447
so I want to know,
one way or another,

386
00:24:52,491 --> 00:24:54,580
where you stand.

387
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,761
You're right.

388
00:25:01,804 --> 00:25:03,850
I should've told him
to go shove it.

389
00:25:03,893 --> 00:25:07,506
Wouldn't have been
the first time.

390
00:25:09,595 --> 00:25:11,074
He probably
would have tried

391
00:25:11,118 --> 00:25:14,556
to give you
permanent detention,

392
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:17,603
like when
we were in school.

393
00:25:20,606 --> 00:25:24,044
I don't know why
you like me, Jenna.

394
00:25:24,827 --> 00:25:26,046
You're a teacher.

395
00:25:26,089 --> 00:25:27,613
I barely graduated.

396
00:25:27,656 --> 00:25:29,484
You read
the classics.

397
00:25:29,528 --> 00:25:34,489
I'm strictly
simpsonsreruns.

398
00:25:34,881 --> 00:25:38,406
But I couldn't care
about anybody more.

399
00:25:38,449 --> 00:25:41,496
You know that,
don't you?

400
00:25:47,110 --> 00:25:51,680
I like you because
you have a good heart...

401
00:25:51,941 --> 00:25:57,599
And because you're
not afraid to admit
when you're wrong.

402
00:25:57,643 --> 00:26:00,646
That's a very sexy quality.

403
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:16,531
Plus you got
the nicest buns

404
00:26:16,575 --> 00:26:19,882
