the enemy camp,

409
00:26:29,413 --> 00:26:31,154
test the security response,

410
00:26:31,198 --> 00:26:32,547
and then eliminate

411
00:26:32,591 --> 00:26:36,551
as many of the enemy
as possible.

412
00:26:36,856 --> 00:26:39,728
This is a very
unstable unit.

413
00:26:39,772 --> 00:26:41,730
Stopping it might be
extremely dangerous,

414
00:26:41,774 --> 00:26:43,166
especially if
it's locked into

415
00:26:43,210 --> 00:26:45,821
