Yo!

419
00:27:06,712 --> 00:27:08,888
Ooh, foxy mama!

420
00:27:08,931 --> 00:27:10,585
Hoo-hoo!

421
00:28:44,853 --> 00:28:46,986
Sanders and I
thought you and I

422
00:28:47,029 --> 00:28:49,510
should get to know
each other better.

423
00:28:49,553 --> 00:28:50,511
Oh!

424
00:28:50,554 --> 00:28:51,991
Aah!

425
00:28:52,034 --> 00:28:53,470
Aah!

426
