that I want to be
a teacher anymore,

815
00:57:30,838 --> 00:57:32,884
but, uh...

816
00:57:32,927 --> 00:57:34,973
I don't know.

817
00:57:39,934 --> 00:57:43,242
Let's not talk
about it, o.K.?

818
00:57:49,944 --> 00:57:53,339
Doing your duty
is never easy.

819
00:57:53,382 --> 00:57:57,474
