822
00:58:41,213 --> 00:58:43,302
Fuck me.

823
00:58:46,958 --> 00:58:49,047
Jenna!

824
00:58:50,309 --> 00:58:51,571
Sheriff, this is Hazel.

825
00:58:51,615 --> 00:58:54,400
